{
  "texts": [
    "For instance, all comparisons in our current study were conducted using the AZH and Medetec dataset.",
    "Although our model performed commendably on this dataset, the results might not be fully generalizable to all datasets.",
    "Hence, the applicability of our model to other datasets remains an area for further investigation.",
    "It's noteworthy that our study does not solely rely on accuracy as the evaluation metric.",
    "In an attempt to provide a comprehensive evaluation, we also considered other metrics such as precision, recall, and the F1 score."
  ]
}